---
title: Creamy Sausage Stew with Rice and Broccoli
description: This creamy sausage stew is bound to be a crowd-pleaser. It's served with fluffy rice and broccoli florets to cover all nutritional bases. You can even cater for mushroom haters by serving them separately. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-sausage-stew-33beec39.jpg
